"Optional title"
coid,  pid,  N_x,  N_y,  N_z,  csysid
x_1,  y_1,  z_1,  x_2,  y_2,  z_2,  h
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
coid           : Component ID
pid            : Part ID
N_x            : Number of rebar grids in local x-direction
N_y            : Number of rebar grids in local y-direction
N_z            : Number of rebar grids in local z-direction
csysid         : Local coordinate system ID
                 default: global coordinates are used
x_1, y_1, z_1  : Rebar cage corner coordinate 1
x_2, y_2, z_2  : Rebar cage corner coordinate 2
