"Optional title"
coid,  pid,  N,  N_c,  csysid,  α_c
x_0,  y_0,  z_0,  R_1,  R_2
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
coid           : Component ID
pid            : Part ID
N              : Mesh density parameter (see figure below)
N_c            : Number of elements in circumferential direction (only used if α_c  neq  360&deg;)
