"Optional title"
coid
entype_r,  enid_r,  entype_c,  enid_c,  keep
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
coid           : Command ID
entype_r       : Rebar entity type
                 options: P, PS, ALL
enid_r         : Rebar entity identification number
entype_c       : Concrete entity type
                 options: P, PS, ALL
enid_c         : Concrete entity identification number
keep           : Remove from or keep decoupled rebar elements in model
                 options:
                 0 -> uncoupled rebar elements are removed
                 1 -> uncoupled rebar elements are kept in model

