*INCLUDE
"Optional title"
filename
sf_x,  sf_y,  sf_z,  nid_offset,  eid_offset,  pid_offset,  mid_offset,  gid_offset
x_0,  y_0,  z_0,  x_1,  y_1,  z_1
x_x,  x_y,  x_z,  y_x,  y_y,  y_z,  mirror
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
filename       : The path and the name of file to be includedThe path and the name of file to be included
sf_x, sf_y,sf_z: Scale factors for nodal coordinates in x, y and z directions
                 Scale factors for nodal coordinates in x, y and z directions
                 default: 1
nid_offset     : Number to add to all node IDsNumber to add to all node IDs
eid_offset     : Number to add to all element IDs
pid_offset     : Number to add to all part IDs
mid_offset     : Number to add to all material, damage, EOS and thermal property command IDs
gid_offset     : Number to add to all other command IDs
x_0, y_0, z_0  : Start point for mesh translation
x_1, y_1, z_1  : End point for mesh translation
x_x, x_y, x_z  : New direction of x-axis
                 default: (1,0,0)
y_x, y_y, y_z  : New direction of y-axis
                 default: (0,1,0)
mirror         : Flag to activate mesh mirroring (left handed system where z = y * x)
                 options:
                 0 -> no mirroring
                 1 -> mirroring

*INCLUDE_BINARY
filename
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
