x_x, x_y, x_z  : Direction of local x-axis
y_x, y_y, y_z  : Vector needed for the definition of the local y- and z-axis

*INITIAL_MATERIAL_DIRECTION_PATH
"Optional title"
coid,  entype,  enid,  pathid
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
coid           : Command ID
entype         : Entity type
                 options: P, PS
enid           : Entity ID
pathid         : Path ID

*INITIAL_MATERIAL_DIRECTION_VECTOR
"Optional title"
coid,  entype,  enid
x_x,  x_y,  x_z,  y_x,  y_y,  y_z
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
