*MAT_FOAM
"Optional title"
mid,  ρ,  E,  ν,  did
cid,  tsc,  β
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
mid            : Unique material identification number
ρ              : Density
E              : Young's modulus
ν              : Poisson's ratio
did            : Thermal property command ID
