----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
mid            : Unique material identification number
ρ              : Density
E              : Young's modulus, constant or function of temperature
                 options: constant, fcn
ν              : Poisson's ratio, constant or function of temperature
                 options: constant, fcn
did            : Damage property command ID
thpid          : Thermal property command ID
c_01           : Yield stress parameter 1
c_02           : Yield stress parameter 2
c_s1           : Saturation stress parameter 1
c_s2           : Saturation stress parameter 2
B              : Strain hardening parameter
Q              : Activation energy
ε_off          : Strain rate offset
d_1            : Static recrystallization evolution parameter
d_2            : Dynamic recrystallization evolution parameter
d_3            : Recrystallization evolution exponent (plastic strain dependency)
d_4            : Recrystallization evolution exponent (grain size dependency)
d_5            : Recrystallization reduction parameter
Q_rex          : Recrystallization energy parameter
