l_cap          : Grain size cap
l_ini          : Initial grain size
k_l            : Grain size growth parameter
Q_l            : Grain size growth energy parameter
n_l            : Grain size growth parameter
α_p            : Precipitation hardening parameter
β_p            : Precipitation evolution parameter
γ_p            : Parameter controlling how strongly precipitates inhibit the recrystallization process
f_p^max        : Maximum precipitate volume fraction
f_p^0          : Volume fraction where precipitates begin to influence recrystallization
Q_p            : Precipitation temperature sensitivity parameter
n_p            : Precipitation hardening coefficient
