    5.0e4, 5.0e4, 100.0, 0.00001
#end

*MAT_OBJECT
"Optional title"
"object_id", mid, calibration, revision
param=expression,  "description"
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
"object_id"    : Unique name as given in the object library
mid            : Material ID
calibration    : Calibration number
                 options:
                 = 0 -> the latest calibration will be used
                 ne 0 -> the specified calibration will be used
                 default: 0
revision       : Revision number
                 options:
                 = 0 -> the latest revision will be used
                 ne 0 -> the specified revision will be used
                 default: 0
param = expression: Parameter name and an expression defining its value
description    : Optional parameter description

