"Optional title"
mid,  ρ,  E,  ν,  did,  thpid
σ_0,  Q_1,  C_1,  Q_2,  C_2,  cid,  c_dec,  α
β,  m,  T_0,  T_m,  n
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
mid            : Unique material identification number
ρ              : Density
E              : Young's modulus
ν              : Poisson's ratio
did            : Damage property command ID
