coid
R,  h,  m,  k,  F_t,  F_s,  W_t,  W_s
tol
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
coid           : Command ID
R              : Spot weld radius
h              : Spot weld height
m              : Spot weld mass
k              : Spot weld stiffness
F_t            : Failure force - tear
F_s            : Failure force - shear
W_t            : Energy absorption - tear
