tol            : Maximum allowed distance between surfaces to be connected
                 default: tol = 0.2 h

*PROP_THERMAL
"Optional title"
thpid,  α_T,  C_p,  λ,  k,  T_ref,  ε
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
thpid          : Unique thermal property identification number
α_T            : Heat expansion coefficient or ID of a CURVE defining α_T(T)
                 options: constant, fcn
                 default: 0
C_p            : Heat capacity or ID of a CURVE defining C_p(T)
                 options: constant, fcn
                 default: 0
lambda         : Heat conductivity or ID of a CURVE defining lambda(T)
                 options: constant, fcn
                 default: 0
k              : Plastic work heat conversion factor
                 default: 0.9
T_ref          : Reference temperature for thermal expansion
ε              : Thermal emissivity
                 default: 1

