*TIME
t_term,  sf_Δt,  Δt_min,  Δt_max,  ms_max,  t_start
----------------------------------------------------------------
Variable         Description
t_term         : Termination time or termination FUNCTION
                 options: constant, fcn
sf_Δt          : Time step scale factor. It should range between 0 and 1
                 default: 0.9
Δt_min         : Minimum time step size or time step FUNCTION
                 default: 0
Δt_max         : Maximum allowed time step size or FUNCTION
                 default: 1.0e10
ms_max         : Maximum allowed mass scaling factor on element level
                 default: 1.0e10
t_start        : Start time
                 default: 0

